                                                                                                                <comments>
                            <comment id="14026228" author="dbeech" created="Tue, 10 Jun 2014 08:01:23 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Wouldn&apos;t this cause problems for users that might want to exclude mockito from their mrunit dependency to use an even later version for their own tests?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14251187" author="brocknoland" created="Thu, 18 Dec 2014 05:02:19 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;If we relocated mockito then users could use a completely different version of mockito.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14251197" author="brocknoland" created="Thu, 18 Dec 2014 05:12:47 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I don&apos;t think we can relocate mockito since we expose mocked classes:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://mrunit.apache.org/documentation/javadocs/1.1.0/org/apache/hadoop/mrunit/mapreduce/MapDriver.html#getContext(&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://mrunit.apache.org/documentation/javadocs/1.1.0/org/apache/hadoop/mrunit/mapreduce/MapDriver.html#getContext(&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;perhaps we just mark it optional.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14263243" author="mcdonaldnoland" created="Fri, 2 Jan 2015 21:26:25 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Making mockito-core optional.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14263244" author="mcdonaldnoland" created="Fri, 2 Jan 2015 21:26:54 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I&apos;ve submitted a change to make it optional.  Let me know if this is what you had intended.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14263675" author="brocknoland" created="Sat, 3 Jan 2015 23:37:42 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Thank you! I have committed your contribution to trunk!&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14263682" author="hudson" created="Sun, 4 Jan 2015 00:04:32 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;SUCCESS: Integrated in mrunit-trunk #1126 (See &lt;a href=&quot;https://builds.apache.org/job/mrunit-trunk/1126/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://builds.apache.org/job/mrunit-trunk/1126/&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/MRUNIT-212&quot; title=&quot;Shade mockito dependencies&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;MRUNIT-212&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;MRUNIT-212&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; - Shade mockito dependencies (Mac Noland via Brock) (brock: rev c68c9e45aaf1d17a0e9b4c37a0f739e42def4842)&lt;/p&gt;
